title: Bug 121687: Exception thrown when exporting data in a table within a grid cell
OB: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from a table that is inside a grid cell.
EB: Exporting data from a table within a grid cell should proceed without any exceptions.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Insert one table into one grid cell. 2. Insert another table into the other grid cell. 3. Attempt to export data.
